dc_title_s: Map of Washtenaw County, Michigan from actual surveys by G. R. Bechler & E. Wenig.
dc_creator_sm: Bechler, Gustavus R.,Wenig, E.,Matthias, Benjamin I.,Bechler, Wenig & Company.
dc_description_s: Shows property ownership. "Engraved by B. Matthias." Insets: Chelsea--Saline--Ann Arbor--Ypsilanti--Manchester--Milan--Dexter. Includes business directories, subscribers' names for insets, and 13 vignettes. With vignette of "Barn of Genl. A. Williams, Lima Centre" at lower left. Includes revised land ownership in Lima Township. 1 map: col.; 111 x 120 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
